                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Tips -->
                <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-gray-700 p-4 h-full">
                    <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path></svg>
                        Tips & Panduan
                    </h3>
                    <ul class="text-xs text-gray-400 space-y-2">
                        <li class="flex gap-2">
                            <span class="text-emerald-400 shrink-0">💡</span>
                            <span>Gunakan IP lokal (192.168.x.x) untuk DVR di jaringan yang sama.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-2">
                            <span class="text-emerald-400 shrink-0">💡</span>
                            <span>Pastikan fitur RTSP diaktifkan di pengaturan DVR/kamera Anda.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-2">
                            <span class="text-emerald-400 shrink-0">💡</span>
                            <span>Untuk akses dari luar jaringan, gunakan DDNS atau port forwarding.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-2">
                            <span class="text-amber-400 shrink-0">⚠️</span>
                            <span>Username & password sesuai dengan akun DVR/APK Anda. Jangan gunakan sembarang.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-2">
                            <span class="text-blue-400 shrink-0">🔒</span>
                            <span>Kredensial Anda disimpan dengan aman di database lokal.</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <!-- Supported Protocols -->
                <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-gray-700 p-4 h-full">
                    <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 7v10c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4V7M4 7c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4M4 7c0-2.21 3.582-4 8-4s8 1.79 8 4"></path></svg>
